## Running the Tests

### Run all unit tests:
```bash
cd /Users/tylerwerr/f25_Discovery
python manage.py test tests.unit_test
```

### Run a specific test class:
```bash
python manage.py test tests.unit_test.DiscoveryWorkflowTest
```

### Run a specific test method:
```bash
python manage.py test tests.unit_test.DiscoveryWorkflowTest.test_complete_discovery_workflow
```

### Run with verbose output:
```bash
python manage.py test tests.unit_test -v 2
```

### Run all tests with coverage report:
```bash
coverage run --source='.' manage.py test tests.unit_test
coverage report
```

